  And we are the ones that want to chose,  
  Always want to play,  
  But you never want to lose.  
  
  Aerials, in the sky,  
  When you lose small mind,  
  You free your life.  
  Aerials, so up high,  
  When you free your eyes,  
  Eternal prize.  
  Aerials, in the sky,  
